<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Login Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .button {
            display: block;
            width: 200px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #4a90e2;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #357ab8;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Confirm Your Login</h1>
        <p>Hello,</p>
        <p>You recently requested to log in to your account. Please confirm your login by clicking the button below:</p>
        <a href="{{confirmationLink}}" class="button">Confirm Login</a>
        <p>If you did not request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 Resend Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
